  <div class="container article-narrow article-body legal-content">
    <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
    <p>Everest World Lifts provides elevator distribution, installation, maintenance, repair, modernization, and consulting services. You can contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">{{ site.supportEmail }}</a> or at {{ site.address }}.</p>

    <h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect information you voluntarily provide through our contact and careers forms, including your name, email address, phone number, inquiry subject, experience, interests, and message.</p>
    <p>Our hosting provider and embedded services may also process technical information such as your IP address, browser type, device information, referring page, and timestamps when you visit or interact with the website.</p>

    <h2>3. How we use information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to inquiries, quote requests, and support requests.</li>
      <li>To assess and respond to career-interest submissions.</li>
      <li>To operate, secure, maintain, and improve the website.</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect our legitimate interests.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Service providers</h2>
    <p>The website is hosted on Netlify, which processes form submissions and technical hosting data. Blog content is managed through Sanity. The contact page embeds Google Maps, which may process technical and usage information according to Google's policies.</p>

    <h2>5. Sharing your information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers that help us operate the website or deliver services, and where required by law or necessary to protect rights, safety, and security.</p>

    <h2>6. Retention and security</h2>
    <p>We retain personal information only for as long as reasonably necessary for the purpose it was collected, legal requirements, or legitimate business needs. We take reasonable steps to protect information, but no internet transmission or storage system can be guaranteed completely secure.</p>

    <h2>7. Your choices and rights</h2>
    <p>You may ask us to access, correct, update, or delete personal information we hold about you, subject to applicable law and legitimate retention requirements. Contact <a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">{{ site.supportEmail }}</a> or follow our <a href="/data-deletion/">Data Deletion Instructions</a> to make a request.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy when our practices or legal requirements change. The effective date shown above indicates the latest revision.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact us</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">{{ site.supportEmail }}</a>.</p>
